	   <tr><td colspan=2>I bought my gate spell in Neriak in the cleric guild.&nbsp;&nbsp;As for true north, i personally think it is a waste of money as there are several in game tricks you can use to figure out which way you are heading.  <br><br>These may not be completely accurate as I don't normally use them myself.  If they are wrong, someone please correct them.  <br><br>1) the clouds in the sky always move west I believe<br>2) if you have a rusty weapon, dropping it on the ground, i think the hilt or blade one always points north<br>3) keep hitting sense heading until it tells you which way you are heading.<br><br>As for 1 and 2, these are just things I have read.  I have not personally tested these, so hey I could be wrong.  If so, I am not looking flames, but corrections so that we can help this fella.  Anyway, good luck and good journey.<br><br>Neckrosis<br>7th DE Necro<br>Bertoxx<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
